  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820390/extras/e48059c213c5282cda5f95d545e16969.avif?t=1746030483\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Seclusion is a psychological horror game  inspired by the backrooms and liminal spaces.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Atmospheric Horror : </strong>You will question your surroundings, with unsettling visuals, unpredictable and surrealist environments, and a constant feeling of dread.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Survival Horror : </strong>Adapt to your surroundings, avoid lurking dangers, and manage your resources carefully if you want to stay alive.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Rich lore : </strong>Find clues that slowly reveal the twisted history behind this world.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820390/extras/efc4f0ffc44abab748bd1d48ca4f38f6.avif?t=1746030483\" width=600 height=100 /></span><strong>Embark on a deeply personal journey through a world twisted by traumas, sorrow, guilt and fear.</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Challenging Exploration : </strong>Navigate through eerie, atmospheric environments while solving puzzles that blocks your path.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Evade & Outsmart : </strong>Stay one step ahead of the <strong>Unique entities</strong> as you explore deeper into the unknown.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Uncover the Mystery : </strong>Piece together the story as you move forward, revealing the dark secrets of this place.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820390/extras/3e67a6de808de83fa0debce5b3e1290a.poster.avif?t=1746030483\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820390/extras/3e67a6de808de83fa0debce5b3e1290a.webm?t=1746030483\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820390/extras/3e67a6de808de83fa0debce5b3e1290a.mp4?t=1746030483\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820390/extras/beb2bf4dfac9b8f26406e1a12a7a07af.avif?t=1746030483\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXPLORER MODE AND MULTIPLAYER HAS BEEN DELAYED AND ISN'T YET AVAILABLE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Team up with friends or venture alone in procedurally generated levels where every run brings new challenges and dangers.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Procedurally Generated Worlds : </strong>Each playthrough is different, offering fresh environments, puzzles, and surprises.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Co-op Survival : </strong>Work together with up to 5 players to survive shifting environments and unpredictable threats.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dynamic gameplay : </strong>Plan, Explore, and adapt as you encounter new obstacles and entities on every run.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>In-game proximity voice chat</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Remember to wishlist and follow the game if you want to play it</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Together, we will find a way.</strong></p>",
